{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Kind of semantic tokens which will wrap a combination of "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSTokensSemantic\/documentation\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/FontSizeSemanticToken","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" depending to size classes."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Allows to gather the multiple-value tokens from Figma inside one object.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"If a font size exists with its value depending to the size class, it must be packed in such "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSTokensSemantic\/documentation\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/MultipleFontSizeSemanticTokens"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSTokensSemantic\/documentation\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/MultipleFontSizeSemanticTokens"},"topicSections":[{"generated":true,"anchor":"Initializers","identifiers":["doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSTokensSemantic\/documentation\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/MultipleFontSizeSemanticTokens\/init(_:)","doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSTokensSemantic\/documentation\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/MultipleFontSizeSemanticTokens\/init(compact:regular:)"],"title":"Initializers"},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSTokensSemantic\/documentation\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/MultipleFontSizeSemanticTokens\/compact","doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSTokensSemantic\/documentation\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/MultipleFontSizeSemanticTokens\/regular"],"title":"Instance Properties","anchor":"Instance-Properties","generated":true},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSTokensSemantic\/documentation\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/MultipleFontSizeSemanticTokens\/isEqual(_:)"],"title":"Instance Methods","generated":true,"anchor":"Instance-Methods"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"final"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"class","